<tr>
<td width=50%><font color=white>Posted By: Jeskola Corpseshredder</font></td><td width=50% align=right><font color=white>2000-01-11 07:22:00</font></td></tr><tr>
<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>basically, the berserker proc on the pgt is a lvl 20 enchanter spell. this is a lvl 39 one.<BR>
<BR>
Weapon: PGT<BR>
ProcName:  Berserker Strength.<BR>
-Actual Effects-<BR>
Increase Stat: Strength +25. <BR>
Decrease Stat: Agility - 10. <BR>
Target: Protective Skin: 30 - 50 Dmg<BR>
<BR>
Weapon: Axe of Slayers<BR>
ProcName:  Rampage.<BR>
-Actual Effects-<BR>
Increase Stat: Strength +40. <BR>
Decrease Stat: Agility -15.<BR>
Protective Skin: 200 - 300 Hp.<BR>
<BR>
with this proc, a warrior can scale a little str equipment back and decide if they wanna go heavier on AGI equipment to make up for the negative, dex to help the proc and crit., or AC.<BR>
</font></td></tr></table>
